                Text("Cookies and similar technologies\nWe may use cookies and similar technologies to help personalize your experience. You can adjust your settings to determine which cookies you do or do not allow. Changing your settings and/or deleting existing cookies may affect the Services or your experience of the Site/s.\n\nDirectly\nDRN1 listeners who sign up to the DRN1 news letter, competition, or members area will directly provide information for DRN1 to administer Services.\nEnd Users may also choose to provide information directly to DRN1 and its Customers through the Services and/or Third Party Services.\n\nConnecting third party services\nEnd Users may opt-in to sharing additional Personal Information from third party social and music services such as Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, Deezer, Spotify, Apple Music, and other similar apps.\n\nRemoving third party services\nIf you have connected your Apple Music, Deezer, Spotify, YouTube or another account to the DRN1 App from a landing page and would like to remove access, you can remove access by logging into your music service and deleting the access from the apps section.\n\nFrom advertising publishers\nIn certain advertising products such as sponsored songs, DRN1’s publishing and streaming partners share non-identifiable information about how End Users interact with its advertising products. All partners that share data with DRN1 must be in compliance with this Privacy Notice and retain a privacy policy that is in accordance with applicable laws.\n\n")
