                Text("Changes").underline()
                Text("When visiting this Site/s and/or using our Services, you shall be asked to accept the terms of this Privacy Notice. If you do not agree with the terms hereof, please do not use the Site/s and/or Services. We may update this Privacy Notice from time to time – we encourage you to review it periodically. By continuing to access or use the Site/s and/or Services after those changes become effective, you agree to be bound by the revised privacy notice; if we have your email we will notify you of such changes. We will post the updated Privacy Notice on this page. Please come back to this page periodically to make sure you are familiar with the latest version. Any new Privacy Notice will be effective from the date it is accepted by you.\n")
